import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

# Set professional style and font size
plt.style.use('seaborn-v0_8-whitegrid')

fig, ax = plt.subplots()

# Plot x vs y with different colors for categories
for category in df['category'].unique():
    cat_df = df[df['category'] == category]
    ax.plot(cat_df['x'], cat_df['y'], label=category)

# Set title, labels, and legend
ax.set_title('Line Plot of x vs y')
ax.set_xlabel('x')
ax.set_ylabel('y')
